ğŸ”¹ Step 7: Summary
Concept	Explanation
Hoisting	JS code ke run hone se pehle sab declarations memory me jaate hain
Declaration Function	Pure function ko memory me store karta hai
Expression Function / Arrow Function	Sirf variable ka naam reserve karta hai, function assign nahi karta
Result	Declaration ko pehle call kar sakte ho, Expression ko nahi